fields.name: Estimated cost
fields.formula:
field("Supplies cost") + 
lookup("Venue","Cost per hour") * field("Est. duration in hrs") + 
lookup("Entertainment","Price") * field("Est. duration in hrs") + 
lookup("Catering company","Price") * field("# of attendees")
